# PHASE 1: SHELL & GLOBAL LAYOUT

## Test 1.1: Extract GlobalNav Measurements
- [ ] Navigate to DocuSign Navigator page
- [ ] Extract GlobalNav height (should be ~64px)
- [ ] Extract GlobalNav padding
- [ ] Extract nav item spacing and font sizes
- [ ] Document logo placement and user menu position
- [ ] Take screenshot for reference

## Test 1.2: Extract LocalNav (Sidebar) Measurements
- [ ] Measure sidebar width (expanded state)
- [ ] Measure nav item heights
- [ ] Document section spacing and dividers
- [ ] Extract font sizes for nav items
- [ ] Document icon sizes and spacing
- [ ] Note any collapsed state dimensions if accessible

## Test 1.3: Extract Content Area Constraints
- [ ] Measure content area padding from sidebar
- [ ] Document max-width constraints (if any)
- [ ] Extract scroll behavior and sticky elements
- [ ] Document spacing between sidebar and content

